      code.language-markup
        | &lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;
        | &lt;html&gt;
        |   &lt;head&gt;
        |     &lt;meta charset="utf-8"&gt;
        |     &lt;title&gt;The utf-8, I speak!&lt;/title&gt;
        |   &lt;/head&gt;
        | &lt;/html&gt;